{
  "texts": [
    "We hypothesize that this deterioration occurs because too many history profiles may introduce unrelated or outdated samples, hindering effective personalization.",
    "In most cases, only a small number of history data would lead to a good performance for CHAMELEON.",
    "Limitations.",
    "While CHAMELEON successfully delivers scalable personalization with minimal costs, it has some limitations.",
    "A key challenge is its dependence on the quality of the self-generated preference data."
  ]
}